Package: framerrr
Title: Framework That Increases Portability Decreases Maintenance Errors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Mick",
           family = "Mioduszewski",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mick@mioduszewski.net",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8479-9336"))
Description: Framerrr makes it easier to prevent bugs when porting between environments by separating environment dependent information in configuration files. Files paths are logical and not physically hard coded. Provides helper functions easing common problems in cross-environment software.
